DORSUM OF PROSOMA. Yellowish brown, with longitudinal dark brown band. Cervical groove distinct, radial furrows indistinct (
Fig. 1G
).

OPISTHOSOMA. Oval, dorsum with two pairs of sigillae, yellowish brown, with several irregular black markings (
Fig. 1G
). Venter of opisthosoma yellowish brown, with black markings.
